{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2482 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2482 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"pos":[597,617],"content":"Compiler Error C2482","linkify":"Compiler Error C2482","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2482","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"'identifier' : dynamic initialization of 'thread' data not allowed","pos":[618,684]},{"content":"Variables declared with the <ph id=\"ph1\">`thread`</ph> attribute cannot be initialized with an expression that requires run-time evaluation.","pos":[691,813],"source":"Variables declared with the `thread` attribute cannot be initialized with an expression that requires run-time evaluation."},{"content":"A static expression is required to initialize <ph id=\"ph1\">`thread`</ph> data.","pos":[814,874],"source":" A static expression is required to initialize `thread` data."},{"content":"The following sample generates C2482:","pos":[881,918]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2482 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2482\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2482\"\nms.assetid: 98c87da2-625c-4cc2-9bf7-78d15921e779\ncaps.latest.revision: 9\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2482\n'identifier' : dynamic initialization of 'thread' data not allowed  \n  \n Variables declared with the `thread` attribute cannot be initialized with an expression that requires run-time evaluation. A static expression is required to initialize `thread` data.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2482:  \n  \n```  \n// C2482.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \n#define Thread __declspec( thread )  \nThread int tls_i = tls_i;   // C2482  \n  \nint j = j;   // OK in C++; C error  \nThread int tls_i = sizeof( tls_i );   // Okay in C and C++  \n```"}